OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police has admitted
OL,8,Fduring a public inquiry that mistakes
OL,9,Fwere made when triple killer Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane broke into two students flats
OL,11,Fyears before the Nottingham attacks.
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard that one incident,
OL,14,Fin which a terrified woman jumped out
OL,15,Fof a window to escape him in May 2020,
OL,16,Fshould have been treated more
OL,17,Fseriously.
OL,19,FShe suffered spinal injuries and
OL,20,Fneeded surgery as a result of trying
OL,21,Fto escape.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThe police officers who investigated
OL,8,Fboth incidents told the inquiry that
OL,9,Fthey were not treated as connected at
OL,10,Fthe time.
OL,12,FCalocane also tried to break into
OL,13,Fanother of his neighbours flats while
OL,14,Fhe was a student at the University of
OL,15,FNottingham and living in Brook Court
OL,16,Fin Radford.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FIt was three years before Calocane
OL,8,Fwent on to carry out the Nottingham
OL,9,Fattacks which killed Barnaby Webber
OL,10,Fand Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,11,F65 year old caretaker Ian Coates.
OL,13,FHe also attempted to kill three other
OL,14,Fpeople after running them over during
OL,15,Fthe attacks in June 2023.
OL,17,FSergeant Stephen Swift from
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Police told the
OL,19,Finquiry that "the two incidents should
OL,20,Fhave been linked".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police sergeant Katie
OL,8,FSparks, who was supervising the
OL,9,Fofficer who dealt with the incident in
OL,10,FMay 2020, gave evidence to the inquiry.
OL,12,FMs Sparks said she decided not to
OL,13,Frefer the case to the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service (CPS) based on an
OL,15,Femail she read from Dr Faizal Seedat,
OL,16,Ffrom the Highbury Hospital in
OL,17,FNottingham, a mental health facility
OL,18,Fwhere Calocane had been detained.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FBarrister Julian Blake, from the
OL,8,Finquiry's team counsel, asked Ms
OL,9,FSparks whether the case should have
OL,10,Fbeen referred to the CPS based on the
OL,11,Fpolicy, considering the incident
OL,12,Finvolved grievous bodily harm and
OL,13,FCalocane's mental health was a factor.
OL,15,FMs Sparks replied: "Yes, it should."
OL,26,@wD@TOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FAsked if it was usual for cases of
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm not to be
OL,9,Freferred to the CPS, Ms Sparks said:
OL,10,F"I wouldn't say it's usual. But using
OL,11,Fthe evidence that I had at the time,
OL,12,Fthat was the decision I made.
OL,14,F"It didn't feel like it met the test
OL,15,Fto take it to CPS. And there is an
OL,16,Fexpectation by the CPS on supervisors
OL,17,Fthat only when it reaches that test
OL,18,Fdoes it get referred to them,
OL,19,Fregardless of the seriousness of any
OL,20,Foffence."
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FShe said an email from Dr Seedat,
OL,8,Fwhich said Calocane had no
OL,9,Frecollection of the offence, was
OL,10,Fsufficient for her to make her
OL,11,Fdecision at the time, but on
OL,12,Freflection she could have got more
OL,13,Fdetails from him.
OL,15,FMs Sparks said: "That email provided
OL,16,Finformation that I felt therefore made
OL,17,Fit impossible to take to the CPS to
OL,18,Fget that decision. Therefore it halted
OL,19,Fthe investigation at that point."
OL,26,@wD@QOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FMs Sparks denied that there was
OL,8,F"reluctance" from the Nottinghamshire
OL,9,Fforce to pass cases to the CPS that
OL,10,F"relate to relatively low-level
OL,11,Foffending involving mental health".
OL,13,FPressed on whether the investigation
OL,14,Fconcluded too quickly, Ms Sparks said:
OL,15,F"All aspects of the investigation were
OL,16,Fin place at the time.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUsD@bO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772549421
OL,3,C'Mistakes made by police' in handling
OL,4,Cof crimes years before Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,F"I needed to make that decision, and I
OL,8,Fmade it using the information I had
OL,9,Fbefore me at the time, which was the
OL,10,Fvictim's account, witness accounts,
OL,11,FCCTV inquiries. And that was the
OL,12,Fdecision I made."
OL,14,FThe inquiry will continue on Tuesday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@QO]
